Package: dde-file-manager-git-extension
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         dde-file-manager,
         dde-file-manager-git-service (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: Git extension for Deepin File Manager
 This package provides the Git extension for Deepin File Manager,
 including emblems and menu operations.
 .
 This is the lightweight frontend package that integrates with
 the file manager interface.

Package: dde-file-manager-git-service
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         git,
         dbus-user-session | dbus-x11
Suggests: dde-file-manager-git-extension
Description: Git status service for Deepin File Manager
 This package provides the Git status monitoring service that
 runs as a user daemon to track Git repository changes.
 .
 Features include:
  * Real-time Git status monitoring
  * DBus interface for status queries
  * Efficient multi-repository support
  * Automatic service management

Package: dde-file-manager-vcs-plugin
Architecture: any
Depends: dde-file-manager-git-extension (= ${binary:Version}),
         dde-file-manager-git-service (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Git version control plugin for Deepin File Manager (metapackage)
 This is a metapackage that installs both the Git extension and service
 components for Deepin File Manager.
 .
 This package provides backward compatibility and convenient installation
 of the complete Git integration functionality. 